4314.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4314.description: When Nella invites a group of Chomplings to sleep over in the Clubhouse, they cramp Blaine's style. Until he realizes the real reason they need a home. // Nella must rescue Blaine when his tall tales become an unexpected reality.

4315.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4315.description: Riley secretly enlists the help of a music loving dragon to play a duet with Nella in her big recital. // Dwayne is nervous about going on his first quest as Blaine's steed.

10412.title: Nella The Princess Knight
10412.description: Nella helps Cici learn how to stand up and stand out when Tricksy tries to steal a sparkly trophy. // Too big to fit on the fair rides, a giant ogre shrinks himself using a magical wishing wagon.

10413.title: Nella The Princess Knight
10413.description: Nella journeys to Riley's kingdom in search of a special glowfruit for King Dad's surprise birthday cake. // When Gork dresses as Nella for a costume party, a villain mistakes him for the real princess knight.

16965.title: Nella The Princess Knight
16965.description: Nella helps Queen Mom and Grammy on a hazardous journey to a prestigious sports tournament. // Riley invites Nella on a tour of her kingdom but is more interested in getting a winning picture than enjoying the sights with her friend.

16966.title: Nella The Princess Knight
16966.description: When Castlehaven loses its sparkle, Nella and the Knights of the Sparkly Table face their toughest quest yet to get it back. // Nella's family vacation to Lake Twinkle is interrupted by Tricksy.

23535.title: Nella The Princess Knight
23535.description: A wild orc disrupts Nella's concert. // Blaine thinks he can do everything better than Nella and sets out to prove it by finding the famous Pink Polka Dotted Dragon Egg.

23536.title: Nella The Princess Knight
23536.description: When Clod loses his invitation to the Royal Cafe Breakfast Buffet, Nella dubs him 'Sir Clod The Finder'. // When a luminous phoenix shines brightly across the kingdom, it keeps Blaine up for days. Nella tries to help him.

29968.title: Nella The Princess Knight
29968.description: The kingdom is taken over by sleepy dragons who have been forced out of their home by a monster. // Nella's wild friend Minatori wants to play hide and seek, but she is unwilling to follow Nella's House Rules.

29969.title: Nella The Princess Knight
29969.description: A dragon is scaring the kingdom, and Nella sets off to stop her - only to discover that the dragon has just been trying to make friends. // When troublesome impkins storm the ice cream parlor, it's up to Nella to save the day.

36696.title: Nella The Princess Knight
36696.description: A new girl moves to the kingdom - with a big secret to hide. // Nella tracks down Garrett's childhood dragon friend for a birthday surprise.

36697.title: Nella The Princess Knight
36697.description: When Nella's messenger falcon Flutter mishears her dictating the invitations to Clod's Birthday Party, she delivers some very confusing messages to her guests. // Chaos ensues on the day of the Castlehaven bowling tournament!

43368.title: Nella The Princess Knight
43368.description: Trinket gets competitive when she and Clod face off in a special contest. // Smelgly the dragon is desperate to make friends - and things get out of hand.

43369.title: Nella The Princess Knight
43369.description: It's the day of a big parade, and Trinket refuses to admit that she is ill. // Willow is convinced to enter a gardening contest - and accidentally creates an enormous runaway watermelon.

49578.title: Nella The Princess Knight
49578.description: When Nella and Garrett accidentally ruin Sir Coach's favorite trading card they go on a quest to make him a new one. // A celebrity knight visits Castlehaven - and so does the fearsome dragon he supposedly defeated.

49579.title: Nella The Princess Knight
49579.description: Olivia convinces Minatori that she must kiss a frog to attend a fancy tea party. // Clod lovingly paints pictures of Trinket for the Castlehaven Art Faire - but she doesn't like them!

55824.title: Nella The Princess Knight
55824.description: Blaine becomes jealous of Nella at their school's craft fair. // After entering a talent show, Clod is embarrassed to discover that he doesn't have the same talent as all the other horses.

55825.title: Nella The Princess Knight
55825.description: Trinket gets jealous when Nella spends time with Minatori at the mall. // Nella and Trinket are performing ballet when a near-sighted cyclops crashes their recital.

62482.title: Nella The Princess Knight
62482.description: Sea Dragons threaten to spoil Castlehaven's Beach Day. // During a scavenger hunt, Smelgly is paired with Olivia, who takes advantage of their new friendship.

62483.title: Nella The Princess Knight
62483.description: Nella brings some wild critters to school for show-and-tell, but things soon get out of control. // Two rock giant brothers have a disagreement, leaving Nella's family carriage stranded on top of their bridge.

68977.title: Nella The Princess Knight
68977.description: When Sir Coach embarks on a dangerous quest, Nella tags along and realizes she still has a lot to learn. // Nella helps Smelgly the dragon fulfill her dream of joining the Knight Brigade.

68978.title: Nella The Princess Knight
68978.description: Trinket is desperate to keep things perfect for Royal Family Picture Day. // Nella and Norma's 'Best Sisters' playdate is interrupted by two arguing rock giant brothers.

75409.title: Nella The Princess Knight
75409.description: Nella and Trinket accidently agree to attend both Garrett and Minatori's sleepovers on the same night. // Garrett and Blaine disobey the rules and sneak out at night to see a fantastical star.

75410.title: Nella The Princess Knight
75410.description: Blaine's fancy cousin Olivia visits and questions Nella's ability to be both a princess and a knight. // When Nella loses a knightly contest, she's determined to improve by practicing.

81926.title: Nella The Princess Knight
81926.description: Nella searches for a magical crystal to make it snow for their annual 'Snow Festival'. // Nella and her friends must play as a team to win the Castlehaven gobletball tournament.

81927.title: Nella The Princess Knight
81927.description: While camping with the Knight Trekkers, Blaine goes to extreme lengths to earn his first badge. // Nella finally brings two arguing groups of dragons together, but Trinket accidentally reignites their rivalry.

88300.title: Nella The Princess Knight
88300.description: Nella bravely journeys to track down a wicked wizard, who has taken all of the kingdom's fancy things. But she has to rely on her own inner courage after he takes her knightly heart pendant too!

88301.title: Nella The Princess Knight
88301.description: Trinket is hesitant to enter the Castlehaven Rollerfest until she discovers a pair of 'magical' roller skates. // Blaine gets jealous when Garrett is cast as the part he wants in the big school play.

94176.title: Nella The Princess Knight
94176.description: Flutter gets jealous when Nella asks Flapper to deliver her mail. // Nella must teach three hydra sisters how to take turns before they ruin this year's Harvest Festival.

94177.title: Nella The Princess Knight
94177.description: A selfish giant takes all of the kingdom's water for himself. // When Nella and the gang run out of lemons for their lemonade stand, they embark on a journey of epic proportions to find more.
